OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780704175
OL,3,CFormer Channel 4 News presenter Jon
OL,4,CSnow reveals Alzheimer's diagnosis
OL,6,FFormer Channel 4 News presenter Jon
OL,7,FSnow has revealed he has been
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with Alzheimer's disease,
OL,9,Fthe most common form of dementia.
OL,11,FThe 78-year-old journalist will
OL,12,Fdiscuss the reality of living with the
OL,13,Fcondition in a documentary titled Jon
OL,14,FSnow: A Last Big Story, which will air
OL,15,Flater this month.
OL,17,FIn it, he is said to open up about how
OL,18,Fhe is dealing with the disease,
OL,19,Fsaying: "At the beginning, I wanted to
OL,20,Fhide it, there's so much prejudice.
OL,26,@{D@IOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
