PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780704175
OL,3,CFormer Channel 4 News presenter Jon
OL,4,CSnow reveals Alzheimer's diagnosis
OL,6,F"Any sort of hint of mental decay,
OL,7,Fyou're sort of dead. There are moments
OL,8,Fwhen it pops up but it's not an all-
OL,9,Fday, every-day condition, and that's
OL,10,Fwhat I cling on to."
OL,12,FSnow revealed he has had the disease
OL,13,Fsince 2023, adding that before his
OL,14,Fdiagnosis he was reluctant to see a
OL,15,Fdoctor and insisted there was nothing
OL,16,Fwrong.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@TO]
