PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780704175
OL,3,CFormer Channel 4 News presenter Jon
OL,4,CSnow reveals Alzheimer's diagnosis
OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,7,Fpraised Snow as a "true giant in
OL,8,Fjournalism" in light of his diagnosis,
OL,9,Fand in a post on X he said: "Jon Snow
OL,10,Fhas spent his life asking difficult
OL,11,Fquestions and telling important
OL,12,Fstories.
OL,14,F"Now, in sharing his Alzheimer's
OL,15,Fdiagnosis, he is helping others feel
OL,16,Fless alone and raising awareness of a
OL,17,Fcondition that affects so many
OL,18,Ffamilies."
OL,26,@oD@SOUpD@KO]qD@]OUvD@AOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
