PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780704175
OL,3,CFormer Channel 4 News presenter Jon
OL,4,CSnow reveals Alzheimer's diagnosis
OL,6,FIn an interview with the Daily Mail to
OL,7,Fsupport an Alzheimer's Society
OL,8,Fcampaign, Snow reflected on how he
OL,9,Fstill questions whether he has
OL,10,FAlzheimer's, saying: "I mean sometimes
OL,11,FI doubt whether I've really got it.
OL,13,F"I don't know if it's widespread
OL,14,Fknowledge. I don't feel disabled in
OL,15,Fany way."
OL,26,@rD@VOUuD@AOUwD@IO]
