PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780704175
OL,3,CFormer Channel 4 News presenter Jon
OL,4,CSnow reveals Alzheimer's diagnosis
OL,6,FThe journalist also revealed he was
OL,7,Fpart of a clinical trial for the
OL,8,Fcondition and has previously spoken
OL,9,Fabout how his mother, Joan, struggled
OL,10,Fwith Alzheimer's in the years leading
OL,11,Fup to her death.
OL,13,FAlzheimer's is the ongoing decline of
OL,14,Fbrain functioning and can affect
OL,15,Fmemory, thinking skills and other
OL,16,Fmental abilities, according to the NHS.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
