PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780704175
OL,3,CFormer Channel 4 News presenter Jon
OL,4,CSnow reveals Alzheimer's diagnosis
OL,6,FMichelle Dyson, the chief executive of
OL,7,Fthe Alzheimer's Society, said: "Jon's
OL,8,Fdecision totalk publicly about his
OL,9,Fdementia diagnosis is a real act of
OL,10,Fcourage and his story will resonate
OL,11,Fwith so many.
OL,13,F"His support for Alzheimer's Society
OL,14,Fwill help spark a national
OL,15,Fconversation about dementia that we so
OL,16,Fdesperately need.
OL,18,F"Despite being the UK's biggest
OL,19,Fkiller, dementia is still not treated
OL,20,Fwith the same urgency as other major
OL,21,Fhealth conditions like cancer."
OL,26,@oD@`OUuD@AOUzD@AOU}D@_O]
