PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780704175
OL,3,CFormer Channel 4 News presenter Jon
OL,4,CSnow reveals Alzheimer's diagnosis
OL,6,FMs Dyson added that Snow and his wife
OL,7,Fare "shining a light on the need for
OL,8,Ffaster, fairer access to diagnosis" as
OL,9,Fshe emphasised how important an early
OL,10,Fdiagnosis can be in helping to support
OL,11,Fthose with the condition.
OL,13,FSnow is famed for his decades-long
OL,14,Fcareer as a journalist and TV
OL,15,Fpresenter and known for being the
OL,16,Flongest-running face of Channel 4 News
OL,17,F` which he anchored from 1989 to 2021.
OL,26,@oD@EOUpD@cO]
