PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780704175
OL,3,CFormer Channel 4 News presenter Jon
OL,4,CSnow reveals Alzheimer's diagnosis
OL,6,FLouisa Compton, head of news, current
OL,7,Faffairs, specialist factual and sport
OL,8,Fat Channel 4 said: "Jon Snow is not
OL,9,Fjust one of Channel 4's most
OL,10,Frecognisable faces ` he is part of our
OL,11,Fvery fabric and is dearly loved by
OL,12,Fviewers around the UK.
OL,14,F"It is a profound privilege that we
OL,15,Fare able to document his last big
OL,16,Finvestigation, in a sensitively made
OL,17,Ffilm that frames Jon's current affairs
OL,18,Fnous alongside a new life lived with
OL,19,FAlzheimer's.
OL,26,@pD@TOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
