PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780704175
OL,3,CFormer Channel 4 News presenter Jon
OL,4,CSnow reveals Alzheimer's diagnosis
OL,6,F"We hope this film will go a long way
OL,7,Fto raise awareness of how to live
OL,8,Fwhilst facing a life-changing
OL,9,Fdiagnosis."
OL,11,FThe documentary film will follow the
OL,12,FBafta-winning journalist as he
OL,13,Fnavigates life with the condition, and
OL,14,Fas he undergoes an investigation into
OL,15,Fa Zambian community whose land and
OL,16,Fwater were impacted by a mining
OL,17,Fdisaster.
OL,19,FJon Snow: A Last Big Story will air on
OL,20,FChannel 4 at 8pm on June 20.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@KO]
